data.title: List of international trips made by secretaries of state of the United States
data.text: Country Locations Details Dates 1 Canada Ottawa Accompanied President Bush on a working visit. February 10, 1989 Iceland Reykjavk Met with Foreign Minister Jn Baldvin Hannibalsson.
